2.A

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \frac{{{{\left( {\frac{3}{n} + 2} \right)}^2}.\left( {1 + \frac{2}{{{n^2}}}} \right)}}{{\frac{1}{{{n^5}}} - 4}}\]

 

2.B

\[\lim \left( {\frac{{\sqrt {\frac{1}{{{n^2}}} + \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}} - \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}}}{{\frac{1}{{{n^3}}} + 2}}} \right)\]

 

2.C

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to - \infty } \frac{1}{{{x^3} - {x^2}}}\]

 

2.D

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \frac{{\frac{1}{x} + 1}}{{{x^4} + x}}\]

 

3.Đáp án

A

 

4.Đáp án chi tiết

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \frac{{{{\left( {\frac{3}{n} + 2} \right)}^2}.\left( {1 + \frac{2}{{{n^2}}}} \right)}}{{\frac{1}{{{n^5}}} - 4}} = \frac{4}{{ - 4}} = - 1\]

\[\lim \left( {\frac{{\sqrt {\frac{1}{{{n^2}}} + \frac{1}{{{n^3}}}} - \frac{1}{{{n^2}}}}}{{\frac{1}{{{n^3}}} + 2}}} \right) = 0\]

;

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to - \infty } \frac{1}{{{x^3} - {x^2}}} = 0\]

;

\[\mathop {\lim }\limits_{x \to + \infty } \frac{{\frac{1}{x} + 1}}{{{x^4} + x}} = 0\]
